Version 2.6.0
	
* Start of ChangeLog (08/08/2002)

BUGS FIXED


NEW FEATURES
	* Squeeze multiple zeros out of ALARALib [PW] (08/09/2002) 
	  THIS WILL REQUIRE CHANGE IN MINOR REVISION NUMBER


